719894f-a.title: Manhattan: Franklin Terrace - 26th Street (West)
719894f-a.text:
Franklin Terrace: W. 26th Street, south side, slightly east of Ninth Avenue, showing a row of buildings that face this interior court. The W. 26th Street pavement is in the foreground.
October 15, 1938
George D. Chinn

THIS APPEARS TO BE IN THE WRONG PLACE ON THE MAP. FAIRLY SURE THAT NOTHING THIS INTERESTING EVER STOOD AT THAT LOCATION.
